{"id":480150063,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 year, 2 months","timestamp":1618324065,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/480150063/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"6.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        vector<int> trans;\n        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {\n            if (s[i] == 'I') trans.push_back(1);\n            if (s[i] == 'V') trans.push_back(5);\n            if (s[i] == 'X') trans.push_back(10);\n            if (s[i] == 'L') trans.push_back(50);\n            if (s[i] == 'C') trans.push_back(100);\n            if (s[i] == 'D') trans.push_back(500);\n            if (s[i] == 'M') trans.push_back(1000);\n        }\n        int ret = 0;\n        for (int i = 0; i < trans.size(); ) {\n            if (i == trans.size() - 1) {\n                ret += trans[i];\n                break;\n            }\n            if (trans[i] < trans[i + 1]) {\n                ret += trans[i + 1] - trans[i];\n                i += 2;\n            } else {\n                ret += trans[i];\n                i += 1;\n            }\n        }\n        return ret;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer"}
